andcharm.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/halloween_dessert-3.jpg"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Then, add whipped cream and another layer of cake.\u00a0","name":"Then, add whipped cream and another layer of cake.\u00a0","url":"https://sugarandcharm.com/easy-halloween-dessert#wprm-recipe-63301-step-0-3","image":"https://sugarandcharm.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/chocolate_trifle-3.jpg"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Top the trifle off with a fluffy dollop of whipped cream.","name":"Top the trifle off with a fluffy dollop of whipped cream.","url":"https://sugarandcharm.com/easy-halloween-dessert#wprm-recipe-63301-step-0-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add two eyes for the ghostly top!\u00a0","name":"Add two eyes for the ghostly top!\u00a0","url":"https://sugarandcharm.com/easy-halloween-dessert#wprm-recipe-63301-step-0-5","image":"https://sugarandcharm.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/chocolate_dessert-3.jpg"}],"recipeCategory":["Dessert"],"recipeCuisine":["American"],"keywords":"Halloween Desserts, Halloween Trifle, Mini Trifles","nutrition":{"@type":"NutritionInformation","calories":"86 kcal","carbohydrateContent":"6 g","proteinContent":"1 g","fatContent":"7 g","saturatedFatContent":"4 g","cholesterolContent":"23 mg","sodiumContent":"4 mg","fiberContent":"1 g","sugarContent":"4 g","unsaturatedFatContent":"3 g","servingSize":"1 serving"},"@id":"https://sugarandcharm.com/easy-halloween-dessert#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://sugarandcharm.com/easy-halloween-dessert#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https://sugarandcharm.com/easy-halloween-dessert#webpage"}]}